title: 07/23/21 DPS Hour 3 Kirk Bohls and Brady Quinn
itunes:title: 07/23/21 DPS Hour 3 Kirk Bohls and Brady Quinn
description:
Kirk Bohls talks to Dan about Texas and Oklahoma going to the SEC. Kirk says the Big 12 does not move the needle like the SEC. Brady Quinn tells Dan that he believes Aaron Rodgers will come back and play in Green Bay.
